, and means to feed, nourish, support, sustain, cherish, and strengthen. The \'Alo\' concept reflects our mission to be leaders in the emerging <em>Compassionate Care Model</em> of addiction treatment.\n\n\nOur progressive approach to treatment has everyone feeling the difference the moment they step onto one of our facilities. We feel that traditional addiction treatment can tend to be punitive and oppressive. So we provide a fresh, evidence-based alternative. Giving our clients an alternative to twelve-step based programs is crucial in this regard.\n\n\nWe offer a holistic, integrative approach to healing. Rather than subscribing to the ‘disease concept’ of addiction, which can tend to reduce people to their diagnoses, we address the ‘whole person.’ Each client has a unique story. We provide care using an intensive, big-hearted style of care, which helps us to really get to know, and to properly treat, each client. To this end, we boast over a one-to-one staff to client ratio – one of the highest in the industry!\n\n\nWe understand what makes a treatment center great – the people who work there. Our highly skilled, passionate staff is the single most important ingredient to our success. Each of our staff have been hand-picked for their unique ability to reach and engage with our clients. This is what creates change – the magical moments of connection and transformation that occur between clients and staff, ones that our clients will remember forever.\n\n\nIt is with this spirit of compassion, combined with our staff\'s skillfulness, that we inspire, nurture, and empower our clients to change their own lives.'),(1680,4,'_at_widget','1'),(1681,4,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(1682,4,'ampforwp-amp-on-off','default'),(1683,4,'ampforwp_custom_content_editor_checkbox',''),(1684,23,'_wp_page_template','page-treatment-program.php'),(1685,23,'_aioseop_opengraph_settings','a:6:{s:32:\"aioseop_opengraph_settings_title\";s:0:\"\";s:31:\"aioseop_opengraph_settings_desc\";