r\n                        client is ready to go deeper into the roots of their emotional disturbances only after the fog\r\n                        associated with the first few weeks of being clean and sober has lifted.</p>'),(5039,2927,'_location-item_1_location-item-description','field_5aa3f236ef27b'),(5040,2927,'location-item','2'),(5041,2927,'_location-item','field_5aa3f058ef272'),(5042,2927,'location-item_0_location-item-slider_0_location-item-slider-image','2893'),(5043,2927,'_location-item_0_location-item-slider_0_location-item-slider-image','field_5aa3f130ef277'),(5044,2927,'location-item_0_location-item-slider_1_location-item-slider-image','2894'),(5045,2927,'_location-item_0_location-item-slider_1_location-item-slider-image','field_5aa3f130ef277'),(5046,2927,'location-item_1_location-item-slider_0_location-item-slider-image','2894'),(5047,2927,'_location-item_1_location-item-slider_0_location-item-slider-image','field_5aa3f130ef277'),(5048,2927,'location-item_1_location-item-slider_1_location-item-slider-image','2893'),(5049,2927,'_location-item_1_location-item-slider_1_location-item-slider-image','field_5aa3f130ef277'),(5050,2927,'individual-title','INDIVIDUALIZED CARE MODELS'),(5051,2927,'_individual-title','field_5aa4014f8c9b0'),(5052,2927,'individual-item_0_individual-item-title','Internal Medicine Doctor'),(5053,2927,'_individual-item_0_individual-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5054,2927,'individual-item_0_individual-item-description','<p>Our consulting physician is a long-time addiction specialist, and is able to prescribe and\r\n                            manage medications to best treat any\r\n                            accompanying medical issues. </p>'),(5055,2927,'_individual-item_0_individual-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5056,2927,'individual-item_0_individual-item-image','2907'),(5057,2927,'_individual-item_0_individual-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5058,2927,'individual-item','2'),(5059,2927,'_individual-item','field_5aa400500fa95'),(5060,2927,'individual-section-title','INDIVIDUAL CARE MODELS'),(5061,2927,'_individual-section-title','field_5aa4014f8c9b0'),(5062,2927,'individual-item_0_individual-item-over-description','<p> Our program is not meant for everyone. At the Alo House Outpatient program, we only accept\r\n                        highly motivated people who are willing to fully participate in their recovery, and who are\r\n                        voluntarily seeking treatment. Our specialty is with strict chemical dependency, or light\r\n                        co-occurring disorders, and not primary psychiatric cases. With our extensive network of\r\n                        resources, built upon a combined decades of activity in the addiction community, we provide\r\n                        clients who do not fit our program with quality referrals to settings appropriate for their\r\n                        successful recovery.</p>'),(5063,2927,'_individual-item_0_individual-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5064,2927,'individual-item_1_individual-item-title','Internal Medicine Doctor'),(5065,2927,'_individual-item_1_individual-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5066,2927,'individual-item_1_individual-item-description','<p>Our consulting physician is a long-time addiction specialist, and is able to prescribe and\r\n                            manage medications to best treat any\r\n                            accompanying medical issues. </p>'),(5067,2927,'_individual-item_1_individual-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5068,2927,'individual-item_1_individual-item-image','2912'),(5069,2927,'_individual-item_1_individual-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5070,2927,'individual-item_1_individual-item-over-description',''),(5071,2927,'_individual-item_1_individual-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5072,2927,'individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-title','Internal Medicine Doctor'),(5073,2927,'_individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5074,2927,'individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-description',' <p>Our consulting physician is a long-time addiction specialist, and is able to prescribe and\r\n                            manage medications to best treat any\r\n                            accompanying medical issues. </p>'),(5075,2927,'_individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5076,2927,'individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-image','2914'),(5077,2927,'_individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5078,2927,'individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5079,2927,'_individual-section-item_0_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5080,2927,'individual-section-item','11'),(5081,2927,'_individual-section-item','field_5aa400500fa95'),(5082,2927,'individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-title','assessment & referral'),(5083,2927,'_individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5084,2927,'individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-description',' <p>One of the most important aspects of truly effective addiction treatment is a proper\r\n                            assessment by qualified professionals. Alo House understands that every person is unique in\r\n                            their symptoms and circumstances, and requires specialized planning in their\r\n                            addiction treatment and recovery process. We provide full and comprehensive assessments for\r\n                            each of our prospective clients, so that they receive a level of treatment specifically\r\n                            tailored to meet their individualized needs.\r\n                        </p>'),(5085,2927,'_individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5086,2927,'individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-image','2916'),(5087,2927,'_individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5088,2927,'individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-over-description','<p> Our program is not meant for everyone. At the Alo House Outpatient program, we only accept\r\n                        highly motivated people who are willing to fully participate in their recovery, and who are\r\n                        voluntarily seeking treatment. Our specialty is with strict chemical dependency, or light\r\n                        co-occurring disorders, and not primary psychiatric cases. With our extensive network of\r\n                        resources, built upon a combined decades of activity in the addiction community, we provide\r\n                        clients who do not fit our program with quality referrals to settings appropriate for their\r\n                        successful recovery.</p>'),(5089,2927,'_individual-section-item_1_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5090,2927,'individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-title','assessment & referralPsychiatric Assessment and Follow-ups'),(5091,2927,'_individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5092,2927,'individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-description','<p>Our consulting physician is a long-time addiction specialist, and is able to prescribe and\r\n                            manage medications to best treat any\r\n                            accompanying medical issues.\r\n                        </p>'),(5093,2927,'_individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5094,2927,'individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-image','2918'),(5095,2927,'_individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5096,2927,'individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5097,2927,'_individual-section-item_2_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5098,2927,'individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-title','Case Management'),(5099,2927,'_individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5100,2927,'individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-description',' <p>It is our strong belief that those suffering from addiction need an\r\n                            advocate through the difficult process of early recovery. These early days can be consuming\r\n                            and overwhelming. People need someone who is\r\n                            knowledgeable; who can provide help, guidance, knowledge and support through this difficult\r\n                            time; who can provide comfort and support while the addict focuses on what is most important\r\n                            – their recovery. We provide each client with full and comprehensive case management\r\n                            throughout the entire treatment process: from the first phone call and consultation, to\r\n                            aftercare. We are there every step of the way. </p>'),(5101,2927,'_individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5102,2927,'individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-image','2919'),(5103,2927,'_individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5104,2927,'individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5105,2927,'_individual-section-item_3_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5106,2927,'individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-title','Group Counseling'),(5107,2927,'_individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5108,2927,'individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-description','<p>Group counseling sessions serve as a core aspect of successful alcohol and drug addiction\r\n                            treatment. Group sessions cover a variety of topics such as addiction education, relapse\r\n                            prevention, relationships, and life skills. Groups take place daily, Monday to Friday, and\r\n                            provide safe, structured environments where people can learn about their addiction and\r\n                            receive support and encouragement from others who are also in treatment. All of our groups\r\n                            are run by licensed or certified therapists and counselors who specialize in treating\r\n                            addiction. </p>'),(5109,2927,'_individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5110,2927,'individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-image','2920'),(5111,2927,'_individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5112,2927,'individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5113,2927,'_individual-section-item_4_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5114,2927,'individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-title','Individual Counseling'),(5115,2927,'_individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5116,2927,'individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-description','<p>Individual counseling sessions provide clients with the opportunity to educate themselves\r\n                            about\r\n                            their addiction and work on ways to sustain successful recovery in a one-on-one setting with\r\n                            a\r\n                            licensed therapists, certified chemical dependency counselors, and job counselors.\r\n                            Therapists,\r\n                            counselors and clients collaborate and work together to develop ways to maintain sobriety,\r\n                            prevent relapse, and build a full, responsible life. Each client receives at least one\r\n                            one-on-one session per week. </p>'),(5117,2927,'_individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5118,2927,'individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-image','2921'),(5119,2927,'_individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5120,2927,'individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5121,2927,'_individual-section-item_5_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5122,2927,'individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-title','Family and Couples Counseling'),(5123,2927,'_individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5124,2927,'individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-description','<p>The disease of addiction does not only affect the individual abusing the substance, but the\r\n                            entire family as well. Family groups and private family counseling sessions can provide the\r\n                            addict and his or her loved ones with an opportunity to work on the process of recovery\r\n                            together. What often gets lost in the fights, disagreements, and conflict that often\r\n                            accompany\r\n                            the disease of addiction is the underlying love that family members have for one another.\r\n                            Family\r\n                            counseling sessions\r\n                            provide opportunities for loved ones to connect and fight the illness together, increasing\r\n                            the\r\n                            chances for sustained recovery. </p>'),(5125,2927,'_individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5126,2927,'individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-image','2922'),(5127,2927,'_individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5128,2927,'individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-over-description','  <div class=\"out-text-area\">\r\n                    <p>Family groups and private sessions take place every Saturday, along with a fun family outing,\r\n                        which gives everyone a chance to get to know other people who’ve been through what they are\r\n                        going through, and receive support. </p>\r\n                </div>'),(5129,2927,'_individual-section-item_6_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5130,2927,'individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-title','Recreational Activities'),(5131,2927,'_individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5132,2927,'individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-description','<p>At Alo House Outpatient, we provide our clients with opportunities for numerous experiential\r\n                            and\r\n                            recreational outings. These include yoga, hiking, working out, horseback riding, stand up\r\n                            paddle\r\n                            boarding, volunteering, martial arts lessons, and other fun excursions. We believe that\r\n                            getting\r\n                            people involved in these activities increases the body’s natural endorphin systems, which in\r\n                            turn provide people with a substitute for the soothing ‘pleasure and reward’ properties that\r\n                            alcohol and drugs once provided them with. We believe that helping to get people into their\r\n                            bodies, and out into the world, developing a sense of purpose and connection, is a key to\r\n                            recovery from alcohol and drug addiction. </p>'),(5133,2927,'_individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5134,2927,'individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-image','2923'),(5135,2927,'_individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5136,2927,'individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5137,2927,'_individual-section-item_7_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5138,2927,'individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-title','Drug Testing Program'),(5139,2927,'_individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5140,2927,'individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-description','<p>Comprehensive drug monitoring is an integral component to our\r\n                            Outpatient clients’ care. The level of accountability that is provided by frequent and\r\n                            highly\r\n                            accurate drug testing virtually guarantees that our clients stay sober as long as they\r\n                            belong to\r\n                            our monitoring\r\n                            program. Alo House has partnered with a toxicology laboratory, which – with their\r\n                            state-of-the-art liquid chromatography-mass\r\n                            spectrometry instrumentation and automated laboratory testing\r\n                            processes – provides us with fast and accurate quantitative results.</p>'),(5141,2927,'_individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5142,2927,'individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-image','2924'),(5143,2927,'_individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5144,2927,'individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5145,2927,'_individual-section-item_8_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5146,2927,'individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-title','Professionals Rehab Program'),(5147,2927,'_individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5148,2927,'individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-description','  <p>Alo House offers a ‘Professionals Program,’ geared toward those who have either not lost\r\n                            their\r\n                            jobs, who are wanting to re-enter their profession, or who are otherwise considered ‘high\r\n                            functioning.’ The sober living facility that houses those in the professional program is\r\n                            designed to suit an adult, executive clientele. The recovery program takes place during\r\n                            three\r\n                            nights in the evening, from 6pm until 9pm, and one weekend day. This schedule reflects the\r\n                            fact\r\n                            that people are busy putting their professional houses back in order during daytime\r\n                            hours. </p>'),(5149,2927,'_individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5150,2927,'individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-image','2925'),(5151,2927,'_individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5152,2927,'individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-over-description',''),(5153,2927,'_individual-section-item_9_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5154,2927,'individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-title','Young Adult Program'),(5155,2927,'_individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-title','field_5aa400700fa96'),(5156,2927,'individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-description','<p>Historically, drug and alcohol treatment centers have been geared toward middle-aged\r\n                            professionals. The trend, however, has been that more and more young people are entering\r\n                            treatment for addiction. The treatment industry has been slow to adapt to this changing\r\n                            demographic picture. In particular, there is a widespread problem today of young people who\r\n                            are\r\n                            experiencing a ‘failure to launch,’ who have no experience in the work force, or with any of\r\n                            the\r\n                            basic\r\n                            responsibilities of adulthood. Becoming employed around the age of 17 is an extremely\r\n                            important\r\n                            developmental milestone that is not being hit by young people today. This problem needs to\r\n                            be\r\n                            addressed head-on in this new era of chemical dependency treatment. </p>'),(5157,2927,'_individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-description','field_5aa4007d0fa97'),(5158,2927,'individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-image','2926'),(5159,2927,'_individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-image','field_5aa4009e0fa98'),(5160,2927,'individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-over-description','<p>At Alo House Outpatient, it is our job to help get our younger clients up and running and\r\n                        functioning in the adult world. We do this by teaching them practical life-skills, and\r\n                        accelerating their transformation into adulthood. We believe that we are either reinforcing the\r\n                        problem of ‘learned helplessness’ that so many young people today suffer from, or we are helping\r\n                        them to achieve a state of autonomy. The heart of our work is geared toward helping our young\r\n                        clients achieve the freedom to live their own lives. And we make sure to have some fun in the\r\n                        process — without joy, a sober life is next to impossible. </p>'),(5161,2927,'_individual-section-item_10_individual-section-item-over-description','field_5aa40ba092838'),(5162,2928,'_edit_last','1'),(5163,2928,'_edit_lock','1520804121:1'),(5164,23,'_edit_last','1'),(5165,23,'top-section-title','Treatment Program'),(5166,23,'_top-section-title','field_5aa593cceba22'),(5167,23,'top-section-sub-title','A NEW MODEL OF ADDICTION TREATMENT'),(5168,23,'_top-section-sub-title','field_5aa59542eba23'),(5169,23,'top-section-text-area',' <p>Alo House has created a community-based, luxury, long-term holistic drug &amp; alcohol rehab by\r\n                        running inpatient, outpatient, and transitional living facilities under one umbrella.</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"highlight-text\">These multiple levels of care give us flexibility, and allows us to create\r\n                        ways of making substance abuse treatment affordable to most families. We shepherd clients\r\n                        through the treatment process by helping them to integrate themselves into the fabric of our\r\n                        community, and even more importantly, by focusing on what their lives are going to look like\r\n                        post-treatment.</p>\r\n                    <p>Most treatment professionals have admitted that the old 30-day model is not working The National\r\n                        Institute on Drug Abuse characterizes programs shorter than 90 days “of limited effectiveness.”\r\n                        Affordable, long-term, community-based care that really works is the future of drug and alcohol\r\n                        treatment … And this is what we are committed to providing each of our clients and their\r\n                        families with. The long term treatment model is at the core of our program, but we offer\r\n                        multiple treatment options based on our individualized care model. These include non-12 step\r\n                        rehab &amp; our holistic addiction treatment tracks.</p>'),(5170,23,'_top-section-text-area','field_5aa59560eba24'),(5171,23,'top-section-image-area','2936'),(5172,23,'_top-section-image-area','field_5aa596be59a81'),(5173,2935,'top-section-title',''),(5174,2935,'_top-section-title','field_5aa593cceba22'),(5175,2935,'top-section-sub-title',''),(5176,2935,'_top-section-sub-title','field_5aa59542eba23'),(5177,2935,'top-section-text-area',''),(5178,2935,'_top-section-text-area','field_5aa59560eba24'),(5179,2935,'top-section-image-area',''),(5180,2935,'_top-section-image-area','field_5aa596be59a81'),(5181,2936,'_wp_attached_file','2018/03/treatment-combine-1.png'),(5182,2936,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:454;s:6:\"height\";i:446;s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"2018/03/treatment-combine-1.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"treatment-combine-1-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"treatment-combine-1-250x246.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:250;s:6:\"height\";i:246;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:11:\"large-thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"treatment-combine-1-454x350.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:454;s:6:\"height\";i:350;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:5:\"small\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"treatment-combine-1-120x118.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:120;s:6:\"height\";i:118;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:11:\"staff-photo\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"treatment-combine-1-198x198.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:198;s:6:\"height\";i:198;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(5183,2937,'top-section-title','Treatment Program'),(5184,2937,'_top-section-title','field_5aa593cceba22'),(5185,2937,'top-section-sub-title','A NEW MODEL OF ADDICTI