e underlying causes of one’s pain, and the self-medication that\r\n                                    so\r\n                                    often follows this pain.</p>'),(5528,23,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-text-content','field_5aa625a43fab2'),(5529,23,'individual-care-section-item','1'),(5530,23,'_individual-care-section-item','field_5aa6254d3faae'),(5531,2980,'top-section-title','Treatment Program'),(5532,2980,'_top-section-title','field_5aa593cceba22'),(5533,2980,'top-section-sub-title','A NEW MODEL OF ADDICTION TREATMENT'),(5534,2980,'_top-section-sub-title','field_5aa59542eba23'),(5535,2980,'top-section-text-area',' <p>Alo House has created a community-based, luxury, long-term holistic drug &amp; alcohol rehab by\r\n                        running inpatient, outpatient, and transitional living facilities under one umbrella.</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"highlight-text\">These multiple levels of care give us flexibility, and allows us to create\r\n                        ways of making substance abuse treatment affordable to most families. We shepherd clients\r\n                        through the treatment process by helping them to integrate themselves into the fabric of our\r\n                        community, and even more importantly, by focusing on what their lives are going to look like\r\n                        post-treatment.</p>\r\n                    <p>Most treatment professionals have admitted that the old 30-day model is not working The National\r\n                        Institute on Drug Abuse characterizes programs shorter than 90 days “of limited effectiveness.”\r\n                        Affordable, long-term, community-based care that really works is the future of drug and alcohol\r\n                        treatment … And this is what we are committed to providing each of our clients and their\r\n                        families with. The long term treatment model is at the core of our program, but we offer\r\n                        multiple treatment options based on our individualized care model. These include non-12 step\r\n                        rehab &amp; our holistic addiction treatment tracks.</p>'),(5536,2980,'_top-section-text-area','field_5aa59560eba24'),(5537,2980,'top-section-image-area','2936'),(5538,2980,'_top-section-image-area','field_5aa596be59a81'),(5539,2980,'step-section-item_0_step-section-item-title','Intervention'),(5540,2980,'_step-section-item_0_step-section-item-title','field_5aa59dcd07fcd'),(5541,2980,'step-section-item_0_step-section-item-image','2804'),(5542,2980,'_step-section-item_0_step-section-item-image','field_5aa59e0307fce'),(5543,2980,'step-section-item_0_step-section-item-text-content',' <p>People suffering from alcohol and drug addiction are often in denial of the severity\r\n                                    of their illness, and the tremendous impact that it is has on their lives and the\r\n                                    lives of the people around them. A professional intervention, a guided process by\r\n                                    which family, friends and a trained professional lovingly confront the addict and\r\n                                    their disease, can be highly effective in engaging the person into treatment. </p>\r\n                                <p>The trained and knowledgeable staff at Alo House can provide intervention services.\r\n                                    We can help the individual understand the severity of their addiction, and provide\r\n                                    them with the support, motivation and guidance necessary to receive the treatment\r\n                                    that they desperately need.</p>'),(5544,2980,'_step-section-item_0_step-section-item-text-content','field_5aa59e1a07fcf'),(5545,2980,'step-section-item','2'),(5546,2980,'_step-section-item','field_5aa59d4c07fcc'),(5547,2980,'step-section-item_0_step-section-item-text-area',' <p>People suffering from alcohol and drug addiction are often in denial of the severity\r\n                                    of their illness, and the tremendous impact that it is has on their lives and the\r\n                                    lives of the people around them. A professional intervention, a guided process by\r\n                                    which family, friends and a trained professional lovingly confront the addict and\r\n                                    their disease, can be highly effective in engaging the person into treatment. </p>\r\n                                <p>The trained and knowledgeable staff at Alo House can provide intervention services.\r\n                                    We can help the individual understand the severity of their addiction, and provide\r\n                                    them with the support, motivation and guidance necessary to receive the treatment\r\n                                    that they desperately need.</p>'),(5548,2980,'_step-section-item_0_step-section-item-text-area','field_5aa59e1a07fcf'),(5549,2980,'step-section-title','Treatment Steps'),(5550,2980,'_step-section-title','field_5aa5a2c6ab523'),(5551,2980,'step-section-item_1_step-section-item-title','Detoxification'),(5552,2980,'_step-section-item_1_step-section-item-title','field_5aa59dcd07fcd'),(5553,2980,'step-section-item_1_step-section-item-image','2943'),(5554,2980,'_step-section-item_1_step-section-item-image','field_5aa59e0307fce'),(5555,2980,'step-section-item_1_step-section-item-text-area',' <p>Drug and Alcohol Detoxification, or ‘Detox’ for short, is the process of allowing the\r\n                                    body to rid itself of a drug while managing the symptoms of withdrawal. It is the\r\n                                    first step in a drug treatment program, and should be followed by treatment at a\r\n                                    certified and licensed inpatient facility like Alo House. Detox alone with no\r\n                                    follow-up is not treatment, and usually unsuccessful.</p>\r\n                                <p>Alo House provides full detoxification services on site. Our facility is housed in a\r\n                                    peaceful and very comfortable six-bed home, conducive to beginning recovery. Alo\r\n                                    House is licensed by the Department of Health Care Services (DHCS) as a residential\r\n                                    detox facility. Once the detox process is complete, our clients may begin regular\r\n                                    programing.</p>'),(5556,2980,'_step-section-item_1_step-section-item-text-area','field_5aa59e1a07fcf'),(5557,2980,'individual-section-title','Individualized Care Models'),(5558,2980,'_individual-section-title','field_5aa5adfd75779'),(5559,2980,'individual-section-text-area','  <p>Alo House offers non 12 step &amp; holistic individualized care for different types of people: a\r\n                    youth track, a professionals track, and custom treatment or non-12 step plans for people who don’t\r\n                    easily fall into one category or another. Detailed assessments and evaluations are undertaken upon\r\n                    admission into the program. The clinical team produces treatment plans for each client, in response\r\n                    to the unique set of needs and circumstances of that particular client. </p>'),(5560,2980,'_individual-section-text-area','field_5aa5ae1d7577a'),(5561,2980,'goal-section-title','Goal Oriented Recovery'),(5562,2980,'_goal-section-title','field_5aa5ae347577b'),(5563,2980,'goal-section-text-area',' <p class=\"highlight-text\">Alo House provides a ‘bridge back to reality.’ For each client in recovery\r\n                    from drug and alcohol addiction, the question is always, ‘When does reality begin?’ </p>\r\n                </p>The answers will vary from client to client, but will usually take the form of work, school, and\r\n                long-term plans for the future. In collaboration with the clients themselves, the clinical team, and\r\n                other family members, benchmarks of success are established along the path of recovery. A long-term\r\n                treatment plan emerges from this work. And with a transparent process, everyone can be clear about the\r\n                goals of the recovery process up front. The end goal of the individualized treatment model is to provide\r\n                long-term accountability to our clients.</p>'),(5564,2980,'_goal-section-text-area','field_5aa5ae407577c'),(5565,2980,'box-row_1-title','Young Adult Drug Rehab'),(5566,2980,'_box-row_1-title','field_5aa61f3c3e9e4'),(5567,2980,'box-row_1-text-conent',' <p>At Alo House, it is our job to help get our younger clients up and running and functioning in the\r\n                        adult\r\n                        world. This is done by teaching them practical life-skills, and accelerating their\r\n                        transformation into\r\n                        adulthood. We believe that we are either reinforcing the problem of ‘learned helplessness’ that\r\n                        so many\r\n                        young people today suffer from, or we are helping achieve a state of autonomy. The heart of our\r\n                        work is\r\n                        geared toward helping our young clients achieve the freedom to live their own lives. And we make\r\n                        sure to\r\n                        have some fun in the process — without joy, a sober life is next to impossible.</p>'),(5568,2980,'_box-row_1-text-conent','field_5aa61f823e9e5'),(5569,2980,'box-row_1-image','2963'),(5570,2980,'_box-row_1-image','field_5aa61fa23e9e6'),(5571,2980,'box-row_2-title','Professionals Addiction Treatment'),(5572,2980,'_box-row_2-title','field_5aa61fb93e9e7'),(5573,2980,'box-row_2-text-content','<p>Alo House offers a ‘Professionals Program,’ geared toward those who have either not lost their\r\n                        jobs, who\r\n                        are wanting to re-enter their profession, or who are otherwise considered ‘high functioning.’\r\n                        The\r\n                        facility that houses those in the professional program is designed to suit an adult, executive\r\n                        clientele, and the milieu reflects this specific group. The recovery program takes place during\r\n                        three\r\n                        nights in the evening, from 6pm until 9pm, recognizing that people are busy putting their\r\n                        professional\r\n                        houses back in order during daytime hours.</p>'),(5574,2980,'_box-row_2-text-content','field_5aa61fc63e9e8'),(5575,2980,'box-row_2-image','2964'),(5576,2980,'_box-row_2-image','field_5aa61fd53e9e9'),(5577,2980,'box-row_1-text-content',' <p>At Alo House, it is our job to help get our younger clients up and running and functioning in the\r\n                        adult\r\n                        world. This is done by teaching them practical life-skills, and accelerating their\r\n                        transformation into\r\n                        adulthood. We believe that we are either reinforcing the problem of ‘learned helplessness’ that\r\n                        so many\r\n                        young people today suffer from, or we are helping achieve a state of autonomy. The heart of our\r\n                        work is\r\n                        geared toward helping our young clients achieve the freedom to live their own lives. And we make\r\n                        sure to\r\n                        have some fun in the process — without joy, a sober life is next to impossible.</p>'),(5578,2980,'_box-row_1-text-content','field_5aa61f823e9e5'),(5579,2980,'comprehensive-drug-section-title','Comprehensive Drug Testing Program'),(5580,2980,'_comprehensive-drug-section-title','field_5aa623d6e48a6'),(5581,2980,'comprehensive-drug-section-text-content','  <p>Frequent and comprehensive drug monitoring is an integral component to our clients’ care. The\r\n                        level of\r\n                        accountability that is provided by frequent and highly accurate drug testing virtually\r\n                        guarantees that\r\n                        our clients stay sober as long as they belong to our monitoring program. This drug testing\r\n                        program is\r\n                        monitored by Dr. Lisa Benya, DO, a renowned addictions specialist.</p>\r\n\r\n                    <h3>Best Practices In The Industry</h3>\r\n                    <p> Alo House Malibu has incorporated the industry’s best practices into our drug and alcohol\r\n                        testing program,\r\n                        including laboratory services at three SAMHSA Certified facilities, and two that are dedicated\r\n                        to medication\r\n                        monitoring. SAMHSA, which stands for the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services\r\n                        Administration, is the\r\n                        agency within the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services that leads public health efforts\r\n                        to advance\r\n                        the behavioral health of the nation. SAMHSA’s mission is to reduce the impact of substance abuse\r\n                        and mental\r\n                        illness on America’s communities. At Alo House, we want to provide the best in all areas, to\r\n                        ensure the\r\n                        highest level of safety and care.</p>'),(5582,2980,'_comprehensive-drug-section-text-content','field_5aa623e6e48a7'),(5583,2980,'comprehensive-drug-section-image','2970'),(5584,2980,'_comprehensive-drug-section-image','field_5aa623f6e48a8'),(5585,2980,'individual-care-section-title','Individualized care models'),(5586,2980,'_individual-care-section-title','field_5aa6252a3faac'),(5587,2980,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-title','Holistic Psychiatry'),(5588,2980,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-title','field_5aa625823faaf'),(5589,2980,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-icon','2979'),(5590,2980,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-icon','field_5aa6258d3fab0'),(5591,2980,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-image','2803'),(5592,2980,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-image','field_5aa625a03fab1'),(5593,2980,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-text-content','   <p>Alo House Recovery Centers offers our clients Holistic Psychiatry through our\r\n                                    consulting\r\n                                    psychiatrist, Dr. Meredith Sagan. Holistic Psychiatry can be beneficial to those who\r\n                                    have not seen results from multiple treatment episodes that employed more\r\n                                    conventional\r\n                                    approaches to treating mental health, and for individuals who are searching for more\r\n                                    natural and integrative ways to balance the mind, body, and spirit. </p>\r\n                                <p>Our goal in using Holistic Psychiatry to treat our clients is to reduce their\r\n                                    suffering\r\n                                    and to assist them in restoring their full physical and emotional health, as well as\r\n                                    their balance with the environment. Holistic Psychiatry targets the source of\r\n                                    emotional\r\n                                    disturbances and the underlying causes of one’s pain, and the self-medication that\r\n                                    so\r\n                                    often follows this pain.</p>'),(5594,2980,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-text-content','field_5aa625a43fab2'),(5595,2980,'individual-care-section-item','1'),(5596,2980,'_individual-care-section-item','field_5aa6254d3faae'),(5597,2982,'_edit_last','1'),(5598,2982,'_edit_lock','1520885317:1'),(5599,23,'alumni-program-section-title','Alumni Program'),(5600,23,'_alumni-program-section-title','field_5aa62c9a2db83'),(5601,23,'alumni-program-section-text-content',' <p class=\"hightlight-text\">Addiction recovery is a lifelong process that requires ongoing, continual\r\n                    care. And Alo House\r\n                    wants to be there with you through it all. Alumni meetings take place every Friday evening at Alo\r\n                    House, and are available to all clients following discharge.</p>\r\n                <p> Alumni groups provide former\r\n                    clients with a system where they can continue to receive lasting help and support to continue their\r\n                    successful recovery from addiction. It is so great to get to watch our alumni coming back to welcome\r\n                    and\r\n                    lend a comforting ear to the new people.</p>'),(5602,23,'_alumni-program-section-text-content','field_5aa62ca42db84'),(5603,2985,'top-section-title','Treatment Program'),(5604,2985,'_top-section-title','field_5aa593cceba22'),(5605,2985,'top-section-sub-title','A NEW MODEL OF ADDICTION TREATMENT'),(5606,2985,'_top-section-sub-title','field_5aa59542eba23'),(5607,2985,'top-section-text-area',' <p>Alo House has created a community-based, luxury, long-term holistic drug &amp; alcohol rehab by\r\n                        running inpatient, outpatient, and transitional living facilities under one umbrella.</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"highlight-text\">These multiple levels of care give us flexibility, a