ng them practical life-skills, and accelerating their\r\n                        transformation into\r\n                        adulthood. We believe that we are either reinforcing the problem of ‘learned helplessness’ that\r\n                        so many\r\n                        young people today suffer from, or we are helping achieve a state of autonomy. The heart of our\r\n                        work is\r\n                        geared toward helping our young clients achieve the freedom to live their own lives. And we make\r\n                        sure to\r\n                        have some fun in the process — without joy, a sober life is next to impossible.</p>'),(5640,2985,'_box-row_1-text-conent','field_5aa61f823e9e5'),(5641,2985,'box-row_1-image','2963'),(5642,2985,'_box-row_1-image','field_5aa61fa23e9e6'),(5643,2985,'box-row_2-title','Professionals Addiction Treatment'),(5644,2985,'_box-row_2-title','field_5aa61fb93e9e7'),(5645,2985,'box-row_2-text-content','<p>Alo House offers a ‘Professionals Program,’ geared toward those who have either not lost their\r\n                        jobs, who\r\n                        are wanting to re-enter their profession, or who are otherwise considered ‘high functioning.’\r\n                        The\r\n                        facility that houses those in the professional program is designed to suit an adult, executive\r\n                        clientele, and the milieu reflects this specific group. The recovery program takes place during\r\n                        three\r\n                        nights in the evening, from 6pm until 9pm, recognizing that people are busy putting their\r\n                        professional\r\n                        houses back in order during daytime hours.</p>'),(5646,2985,'_box-row_2-text-content','field_5aa61fc63e9e8'),(5647,2985,'box-row_2-image','2964'),(5648,2985,'_box-row_2-image','field_5aa61fd53e9e9'),(5649,2985,'box-row_1-text-content',' <p>At Alo House, it is our job to help get our younger clients up and running and functioning in the\r\n                        adult\r\n                        world. This is done by teaching them practical life-skills, and accelerating their\r\n                        transformation into\r\n                        adulthood. We believe that we are either reinforcing the problem of ‘learned helplessness’ that\r\n                        so many\r\n                        young people today suffer from, or we are helping achieve a state of autonomy. The heart of our\r\n                        work is\r\n                        geared toward helping our young clients achieve the freedom to live their own lives. And we make\r\n                        sure to\r\n                        have some fun in the process — without joy, a sober life is next to impossible.</p>'),(5650,2985,'_box-row_1-text-content','field_5aa61f823e9e5'),(5651,2985,'comprehensive-drug-section-title','Comprehensive Drug Testing Program'),(5652,2985,'_comprehensive-drug-section-title','field_5aa623d6e48a6'),(5653,2985,'comprehensive-drug-section-text-content','  <p>Frequent and comprehensive drug monitoring is an integral component to our clients’ care. The\r\n                        level of\r\n                        accountability that is provided by frequent and highly accurate drug testing virtually\r\n                        guarantees that\r\n                        our clients stay sober as long as they belong to our monitoring program. This drug testing\r\n                        program is\r\n                        monitored by Dr. Lisa Benya, DO, a renowned addictions specialist.</p>\r\n\r\n                    <h3>Best Practices In The Industry</h3>\r\n                    <p> Alo House Malibu has incorporated the industry’s best practices into our drug and alcohol\r\n                        testing program,\r\n                        including laboratory services at three SAMHSA Certified facilities, and two that are dedicated\r\n                        to medication\r\n                        monitoring. SAMHSA, which stands for the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services\r\n                        Administration, is the\r\n                        agency within the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services that leads public health efforts\r\n                        to advance\r\n                        the behavioral health of the nation. SAMHSA’s mission is to reduce the impact of substance abuse\r\n                        and mental\r\n                        illness on America’s communities. At Alo House, we want to provide the best in all areas, to\r\n                        ensure the\r\n                        highest level of safety and care.</p>'),(5654,2985,'_comprehensive-drug-section-text-content','field_5aa623e6e48a7'),(5655,2985,'comprehensive-drug-section-image','2970'),(5656,2985,'_comprehensive-drug-section-image','field_5aa623f6e48a8'),(5657,2985,'individual-care-section-title','Individualized care models'),(5658,2985,'_individual-care-section-title','field_5aa6252a3faac'),(5659,2985,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-title','Holistic Psychiatry'),(5660,2985,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-title','field_5aa625823faaf'),(5661,2985,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-icon','2979'),(5662,2985,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-icon','field_5aa6258d3fab0'),(5663,2985,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-image','2803'),(5664,2985,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-image','field_5aa625a03fab1'),(5665,2985,'individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-text-content','   <p>Alo House Recovery Centers offers our clients Holistic Psychiatry through our\r\n                                    consulting\r\n                                    psychiatrist, Dr. Meredith Sagan. Holistic Psychiatry can be beneficial to those who\r\n                                    have not seen results from multiple treatment episodes that employed more\r\n                                    conventional\r\n                                    approaches to treating mental health, and for individuals who are searching for more\r\n                                    natural and integrative ways to balance the mind, body, and spirit. </p>\r\n                                <p>Our goal in using Holistic Psychiatry to treat our clients is to reduce their\r\n                                    suffering\r\n                                    and to assist them in restoring their full physical and emotional health, as well as\r\n                                    their balance with the environment. Holistic Psychiatry targets the source of\r\n                                    emotional\r\n                                    disturbances and the underlying causes of one’s pain, and the self-medication that\r\n                                    so\r\n                                    often follows this pain.</p>'),(5666,2985,'_individual-care-section-item_0_individual-care-section-item-text-content','field_5aa625a43fab2'),(5667,2985,'individual-care-section-item','1'),(5668,2985,'_individual-care-section-item','field_5aa6254d3faae'),(5669,2985,'alumni-program-section-title','Alumni Program'),(5670,2985,'_alumni-program-section-title','field_5aa62c9a2db83'),(5671,2985,'alumni-program-section-text-content',' <p class=\"hightlight-text\">Addiction recovery is a lifelong process that requires ongoing, continual\r\n                    care. And Alo House\r\n                    wants to be there with you through it all. Alumni meetings take place every Friday evening at Alo\r\n                    House, and are available to all clients following discharge.</p>\r\n                <p> Alumni groups provide former\r\n                    clients with a system where they can continue to receive lasting help and support to continue their\r\n                    successful recovery from addiction. It is so great to get to watch our alumni coming back to welcome\r\n                    and\r\n                    lend a comforting ear to the new people.</p>'),(5672,2985,'_alumni-program-section-text-content','field_5aa62ca42db84'),(5674,2801,'_encloseme','1'),(5676,2801,'_encloseme','1');
